==Administrative divisions==

==={{lang|de|Regierungsbezirke}} (administrative districts)===
[[File:WV-Bavaria regions.svg|thumb|WV-Bavaria regions]]
[[File:Bavarian Admin Districts.jpg|thumb|Administrative Districts (''{{lang|de|Regierungsbezirke}}'' and ''{{lang|de|Bezirke}}'') of Bavaria]]
Bavaria is divided into 7 administrative districts called ''{{lang|de|Regierungsbezirke}}'' (singular ''{{lang|de|[[Regierungsbezirk]]}}'').

# [[Upper Franconia]] ({{lang-de|Oberfranken}})
# [[Middle Franconia]] (''{{lang|de|Mittelfranken}}'')
# [[Lower Franconia]] (''{{lang|de|Unterfranken}}'')
# [[Swabia (administrative region)|Swabia]] (''{{lang|de|Schwaben}}'')
